Source: pg-roast
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/samirketema/pg_roast

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-roast
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-roast
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Opinionated PostgreSQL database auditor
 pg_roast audits schema design, security configuration, operational health,
 and query behavior. It supports manual audits and periodic background audits.
